<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1437,931,1174]" pageId="27" pageNumber="88">
Originally described from 
<collectingCountry box="[454,579,931,957]" name="Guatemala" pageId="27" pageNumber="88">Guatemala</collectingCountry>
. Records from several South American countries are in the literature; however, some of these records are invalid synonymies proposed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Oliva, A." box="[870,1016,967,994]" pageId="27" pageNumber="88" pagination="87 - 104" refId="ref12701" refString="Oliva, A. (1992) The species of Hydrochus (Coleoptera; Hydrophiloidea; Hydrochidae) described from South America. Bulletin et annales de la Societe royale belge d'entomologie, 128, 87 - 104." type="journal article" year="1992">Oliva (1992)</bibRefCitation>
, for 
<taxonomicName authority="Bruch" authorityName="Bruch" authorityYear="1915" box="[1066,1299,967,993]" class="Insecta" family="Hydrochidae" genus="Hydrochus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="27" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="corruscans">
<emphasis box="[1066,1224,968,993]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="88">H. corruscans</emphasis>
Bruch
</taxonomicName>
(
<collectingCountry box="[1314,1429,967,994]" name="Argentina" pageId="27" pageNumber="88">Argentina</collectingCountry>
) (see 
<bibRefCitation author="Perkins, P. D." box="[203,366,1003,1030]" pageId="27" pageNumber="88" pagination="149 - 167" refId="ref12800" refString="Perkins, P. D. (2019 a) Type designations for Neotropical water beetles in the genus Hydrochus Leach, 1817. (Coleoptera: Hydrochidae). Zootaxa, 4701 (2), 149 - 167. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4701.2.2" type="journal article" year="2019">Perkins 2019a</bibRefCitation>
), and 
<taxonomicName authority="Makhan" authorityName="Makhan" authorityYear="1994" box="[432,642,1003,1029]" class="Insecta" family="Hydrochidae" genus="Hydrochus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="27" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="elsjeae">
<emphasis box="[432,544,1003,1029]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="88">H. elsjeae</emphasis>
Makhan
</taxonomicName>
(
<collectingCountry box="[656,742,1003,1030]" name="Bolivia" pageId="27" pageNumber="88">Bolivia</collectingCountry>
) (Perkins, in prep.). Locality data and deposition records have been published for 
<collectingCountry box="[367,482,1039,1065]" name="Venezuela" pageId="27" pageNumber="88">Venezuela</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Perkins, P. D." box="[497,663,1039,1066]" pageId="27" pageNumber="88" pagination="1 - 59" refId="ref12912" refString="Perkins, P. D. (2019 c) Taxonomy of Venezuelan water beetles in the genus Hydrochus Leach, 1817, and an analysis of male genitalia morphology (Coleoptera: Hydrochidae). Zootaxa, 4708 (1), 1 - 59. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4708.1.1" type="journal article" year="2019">Perkins 2019c</bibRefCitation>
). The one locality data record from 
<collectingCountry box="[1066,1117,1040,1066]" name="Peru" pageId="27" pageNumber="88">Peru</collectingCountry>
is given below. Habitus and male genitalia illustrations are given in 
<bibRefCitation author="Perkins, P. D." box="[594,766,1075,1102]" pageId="27" pageNumber="88" pagination="1 - 59" refId="ref12912" refString="Perkins, P. D. (2019 c) Taxonomy of Venezuelan water beetles in the genus Hydrochus Leach, 1817, and an analysis of male genitalia morphology (Coleoptera: Hydrochidae). Zootaxa, 4708 (1), 1 - 59. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4708.1.1" type="journal article" year="2019">Perkins (2019c</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Perkins, P. D." box="[777,851,1076,1102]" pageId="27" pageNumber="88" pagination="291 - 301" refId="ref12971" refString="Perkins, P. D. (2020 a) Taxonomy of Guatemalan water beetles in the genus Hydrochus (Coleoptera: Hydrochidae). Acta Entomologica Musei Nationalis Pragae, 60 (1), 291 - 301. https: // doi. org / 10.37520 / aemnp. 2020.016" type="journal article" year="2020">2020a</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
